<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="behaviour-n">behaviour <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /bɪ'heɪvjə(r)/    美 /bɪ'heɪvjə(r)/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u">1.★ <strong>[U] 行为；举止：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>This is not a family where <strong>bad behavior</strong> goes unpunished. 
在这个家庭，举止不良逃不过惩罚。</p><footer>译林① – 2</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I think all of us should mind our behavior in public places.
我认为我们大家都应该注意在公共场所的行为举止。</p><footer>2012 福建书面表达</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>(物体等) 反应；性能；行为方式；习性：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the behavior of tin under heat 
锡在受热情况下发生的变化</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Nobody before Jane fully understood chimp behaviour.
在简之前没有人能够全面了解大猩猩的行为。</p><footer>人教④ – 1</footer></div></div>